data.description: This beautiful home offers a combination of ample acreage, water frontage, and thoughtful design making it a truly unique and desirable place. Inside you will find an open concept living space with exposed beams, a well-equipped kitchen, and a designated mud room/laundry room which adds practicality and charm to the interior. Enjoy the privacy of having the primary bedroom on the opposite end of the home, complete with a beautiful ensuite featuring double vanity sinks, a standup shower, and a garden-size tub, creating a comfortable and luxurious retreat. The outdoor features are equally impressive with 8.8 acres of deeded land and 500’ of water frontage that can be enjoyed year round! The backyard is a perfect spot for relaxation along the Warrior River surrounding yourself with nature and serenity, making it a truly picturesque setting. Home features a full house generator! Seller is offering $600 paint allowance.
